de.mdelab.simulator

Class Injection<T extends ArchitecturalElement>

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.mdelab.simulator.Injection<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of model element to which the issue is injected.

    public class Injection<T extends ArchitecturalElement>
extends java.lang.Object
    Specification of an injection of an issue to the model. The injection is going to be performed by the simulator. It specifies the target of the issue and the injector to be used.
    Version:
    0.41
    Author:
    thomas vogel
